title: Fatal shooting at Florida Zombie-themed festival
text: Fatal shooting at Florida Zombie-themed festival Monday, 19 October 2015 The suspect is still believed to be at large. Photo / Supplied One person is dead and at least four others are wounded after a shooting at a zombie-themed street festival in Florida. The suspect is still believed to be at large with Fort Myers police confirming on Twitter an investigation is underway.
